LookAlikes

Fine-Grained Object Counting

Size: 1037 images | Year: 2025 | Status: Released

Counting specific objects when there are multiple visually similar objects in the scene is a challenging task. LookAlikes contains 8 broad categories and 27 fine-grained categories and is designed to benchmark fine-grained object counting. The dataset will be released upon acceptance of the associated paper. If you would like access in the meantime, please send an email.
